                    <p class="block_body">
                        21. For calculating premium and any claim, any
                        <b>contract price</b> in the approved foreign currency shall be converted into Hong Kong Dollar at the
                        <b>specified exchanged rate</b> on the date of the
                        <b>insurable contract</b>.
